37644>>>                // If from child, this is a probably a parent Zoom from a Zoom.
37644>>>                Case Break
37645>>>
37645>>>            Case Else // must be nfUndefined
37645>>>
37645>>>        Case End
37645>>>
37645>>>        Send SetActionButtons
37646>>>
37646>>>    End_Procedure
37647>>>
37647>>>End_Object 
